<p class="page-text">In 2026 in my fifth semester, I created a concept for a scarecrow character called Lonàn. After writing down his backstory, my mentor Even Amundsen prompted me to do my best version of the character 
within one day. What sounded like a very scary task at first, turned out to be a nice exercise to look back after finishing the project. I started with an anatomy warmup the 
next morning and gathered a few references.</p>

